snippet.title: The Bunny Graveyard - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
🐰WISHLIST ON STEAM 🐰
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1892420/The_Bunny_Graveyard/

🐦FOLLOW PICHON GAMES 🐦
https://twitter.com/pichongames

The Bunny Graveyard is a story-rich puzzle RPG where you play as Skye, a bunny who's simply trying to find her brother. Unfortunately, things get ugly once she realizes the world she's living in might not be what it seems...

Some of the gameplay footage in this trailer will be playable in later chapters.
